 <div class="p-4">         <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">
          <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">3</span>
        </h3>
        <p>Giulio ha versato in banca 1 200 euro. Quanto troverà sul conto dopo un anno, se riceve un interesse dell'1,5%?</p>
      </div>

 <div class="p-4 md:col-span-2">         <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">
          <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">2</span>
